n<li>Es darf auf geteilten Speicher nie gleichzeitig geschrieben und gelesen werden, um Inkonsistenzen zu vermeiden.</li>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"semaphore\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#semaphore\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Semaphore</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Integer-Variable <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>s</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">s</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">s</span></span></span></span></span> mit 3 atomaren Operationen\n<ul>\n<li>init(<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>s</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">s</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">s</span></span></span></span></span>, anfangswert)</li>\n<li>wait(<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>s</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">s</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">s</span></span></span></span></span>)</li>\n<li>signal(<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>s</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">s</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">s</span></span></span></span></span>)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Wechselseitiger Ausschluss: <em>Mutex</em> = Semaphor mit anfangswert <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></span></li>\n<li>Mehrere Prozesse im kritischen Bereich erlaubt: <em>Zählsemaphor</em> mit Anfangswert <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span></span></li>\n<li>Zeitliche Ablaufsteuerung:\n<ul>\n<li>Initialisierung\n<ul>\n<li>init(sync, 0)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Prozess A\n<ul>\n<li>Operationend</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Prozess B</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"erweiterte-konstrukte\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#erweiterte-konstrukte\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Erweiterte Konstrukte</h1>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/semester-2/notes/ea7m3dmpg0r5un0f05p627b\">Betriebssysteme und Systemsoftware</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"mnd5f0g7rhonsu64f5fjcrh","title":"2. Semester","desc":"","updated":165524